### Admin API v0.1 - Get Station (happy path)
GET http://localhost:5263/admin/api/v0.1/stations/1
Accept: application/json, application/problem+json

### Admin API v0.1 - Get Station (not found)
GET http://localhost:5263/admin/api/v0.1/stations/0
Accept: application/json, application/problem+json



### Admin API v0.2 - Create Station (happy path)
POST http://localhost:5263/admin/api/v0.2/stations
Accept: application/json, application/problem+json
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Oval",
  "line": "Northern"
}

