Accept: application/json, application/problem+json
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Oval",
  "line": "NotALine"
}

### Admin API v0.2 - Create Station (bad request - invalid enum value)
POST http://localhost:5263/admin/api/v0.2/stations
Accept: application/json, application/problem+json
